### 3. API-First Development ⭐ MANDATORY

**Order** (NO EXCEPTIONS):
1. ✅ Design API contracts (backend + frontend)
2. ✅ Write API contract tests (`@pytest.mark.api_contract`)
3. ✅ Implement APIs
4. ✅ **TEST APIs via curl/requests** (< 1 second) ⭐ CRITICAL
5. ✅ Verify all API tests passing
6. ✅ THEN build UX on stable foundation

**Why**:
- API bugs found during UX = rework both layers
- API testing 60-300x faster than browser testing
- Stable APIs = UX focuses on experience only

